title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-26-2014 WED
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-26-2014 WED




The Glenn Beck Program




The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 2/26/14Wednesday, February 26, 2014 11:04 AM




Glenn kicks off the show with an update on the situation in Boston
     regarding Justina Pelletier, 
         the little girl that has been wrongfully taken away from her parents
           due to their decision to treat her for her illness, 
             in the way that they see fit.  
          The Pelletier's lawyer Matt Staver, 
            Founder and Chairman of Liberty Counsel joins the program
              to give the latest on the situation.

        Also, TX Senator Ted Cruz joins the show 
           to discuss Obama's imperial presidency, 
             the continuation of the IRS targeting of conservative groups,
                and the lawlessness of Obamacare's implementation.

        Plus, Cass Sunstein's plan for conservatives.
